high_descs: Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right, go to the tv stand
Pick up the pencil on the tv stand
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the coffee table
Put the pencil on the coffee stand
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the tv stand
Pick up the pencil on the tv stand
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the coffee table
Put the pencil on the coffee stand
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on the coffee table

high_descs: Turn right, proceed until tv is on left.  Turn right and face tv.
Pick up the right pencil from the tv stand.
Turn around, proceed to center of coffee table on right.  Face table.
Place pencil diagonally on table, between the magazine and tissue box.
Turn right, proceed to tv stand.
Pick up pencil from center of tv stand.
Turn around, proceed to center of coffee table on right.  Face table.
Place pencil on table, diagonally across pen to the right of magazine.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils from tv stand to coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the chair, then turn right and walk to the television.
Pick up the rightmost pencil off of the white table the television is on.
Walk over to the coffee table behind you.
Put the pencil on the coffee table to the right of the book.
Turn right and walk back over to the television.
Pick up the pencil off of the table in front of you.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right again and walk over to the coffee table.
Put the pencil on the coffee table to the left of the book.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils to the coffee table.
